16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 67 O.S. 2021, Section 305, as
18 amended by Section 1, Chapter 189, O.S.L. 2022 (67 O.S. Supp. 2024,
19 Section 305), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 305. There is hereby re-created until July 1, 2025
21 2028, in accordance with the Oklahoma Sunset Law, the Archives and
22 Records Commission, hereinafter referred to as the Commission, to be
23 composed of one member to be appointed by the Governor who shall
24 serve as Chairman, the State Librarian as Vice Chairman and
